Package Model.Request

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CharacterChangeNotification
    Sends a request to the server to change a character
    CharacterDisplayCarrier
    This is an object sent to the user, who sent a CharacterRequest-object, by the server containing the requested character.
    CharacterRequest
    This requests a character from the server
    DisconnectNotification
    This notifies an entity connected to the server-system that a component of the network disconnected
    GetIpCarrier
    This is an object sent to the user, who sent a GetIpRequest-object, by the server containing the requested IP-address.
    GetIpRequest
    This requests an IP from the server
    UserListCarrier
    This is an object sent to the network-participant, who sent a UserListRequest-object, by the server containing the general UserList.
    UserListRequest
    This requests the UserList from the server
    UserRemovalNotification
    This is notifies the server to remove a user from the UserList
